<section xmlns="http://docbook.org/ns/docbook" version="5.0" id="SoftwareBus">
  <title>Software Bus</title>
  <para>
    Csound implements a software bus for internal routing or routing to external software calling the Csound API.
  </para>
  <para>
    The opcodes to use the software bus are:
    <itemizedlist>
      <listitem>
        <para><link linkend="chn"><citetitle>chn_k</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para><link linkend="chn"><citetitle>chn_a</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para><link linkend="chn"><citetitle>chn_S</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para><link linkend="chnclear"><citetitle>chnclear</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para><link linkend="chnexport"><citetitle>chnexport</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para><link linkend="chnmix"><citetitle>chnmix</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
      <listitem>
        <para><link linkend="chnparams"><citetitle>chnparams</citetitle></link></para>
      </listitem>
    </itemizedlist>
  </para>

</section>
